    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/c05889494995f7f64ca072a32d66db71.webp?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/6730a2e1a6f18b3f4cc2fa195e873525.poster.avif?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/6730a2e1a6f18b3f4cc2fa195e873525.webm?t=1758224941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Honji has been accepted to the most prestigious college in the world. To get an edge, he is spending his summer in Kamanori. It's a small town famous for being permanently snowy, and award-winning prep courses. Hopefully nothing goes wrong.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/bcae00736f3051eb9a69f64b565e0e0d.webp?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/e20140366e3a019443be61ee7327bc8a.poster.avif?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/e20140366e3a019443be61ee7327bc8a.webm?t=1758224941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>With plans to just put his head down and study, Honji is taken by surprise with all of the colorful and interesting people he meets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/efb8525327c4f2c9dc447c4e383d61a3.webp?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/77b0de9929770ccf840acc60e57fda9a.poster.avif?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/77b0de9929770ccf840acc60e57fda9a.webm?t=1758224941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Through your choices, you will guide Honji along his path in Kamanori. But BE WARNED, choices are frequent and will have impact on your relationships.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/1052c4d33c59910e2f719effa342dd26.webp?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/a6e6fcd06ca852e52cc34d5e70904d74.poster.avif?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/a6e6fcd06ca852e52cc34d5e70904d74.webm?t=1758224941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In addition to your choices, minigames will often pop up and help you gain favor with the people you meet.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/9bef0b0f3e4754cac1f580d22dc4889f.webp?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/f3c2da156f207123db5e06e5607659a0.poster.avif?t=1758224941\" width=600 height=335 ><source src